Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壯觀！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是神體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來神也會受傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心，水柱會治癒5-O的創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5-O：5A級O.P.A.T.S的略稱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個就是它們的殘骸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的機密資料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是得到採訪許可的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，不允許拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你一直在畫什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，與你無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的話，我可以做你的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的好意，不必了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？你們那裡流行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}蒙古斑：黃種人出生時身上的色斑，多在1、2年後消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古斑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的還在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善哉，善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙，你在忙什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒處理完的事物要完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是放假嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在這裡放鬆享樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是享樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！精神好最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！如月博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上在我家要開一個小聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做學者真是悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚會？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是聖誕夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便慶祝你的升職
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有理由接受你慶賀吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼古板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾和大家聚在一起\N開心一下不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多作戰部的人都會去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如八雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲他也回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都會來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，中你的計了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晚7點恭候各位的光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人好像心情不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是馴鹿似乎不太高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你工作一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，博士！快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，好棒啊！真是太美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有見過雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從來沒有離開過這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有氣象記錄以來的第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會積雪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是明天聖誕夜也下雪就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱朗姆酒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節原本是慶祝冬至的節日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是基督徒們卻擅自把這一天變成了基督的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是無神論者嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗教和宗教活動可完全是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候，當漁夫的爺爺\N和我說他看到了一頭白鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後他對我說「給你這個」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無緣無故地把他心愛的匕首給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次出海捕魚時，\N爺爺就再也沒能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經知道他就要死了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，怎麼想呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有毅力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣努力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了工作而鍛煉體力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿的是什麼衣服啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒帶冬裝！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個，收下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝，謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這是哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…那兒不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧！布奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種事是要負責任的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠！快點起床吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛！像老媽似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據U-06的報告，\ND-1應該已經死亡了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結論還無法斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是聖誕節，不會出問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值班守備沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在如月家好像要舉行晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我無關，說到這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去見見他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，真是白色聖誕節呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定可以看到白色的聖誕樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我第一次在雪地上留下腳印…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒傷著吧，惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然，這個鞋跟太高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次會受傷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…在我這個年紀…\N差不多就有這麼高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹明天就要到這兒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會送禮物給你姐姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:08:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是那麼討厭她，我姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很完美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她也有像一般女孩那樣比較笨的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前，好像有一個她非常喜歡的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像無法忘記他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能送給他的禮物還珍藏在她的抽屜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事她一直無法忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很蠢是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她還是一個小女孩似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得綾人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個，請收下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看看裡面是什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！正是我想要的那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，那個…\N今天晚上在如月博士家的聚會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！我打算去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠也去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天晚上見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…果然八雲喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？我想不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能像姐姐的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，惠和遙非常像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給人的感覺，還有表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周擊毀的D-1的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還沒有失去分子結合力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表明某個保持著功能的部分\N很可能仍潛伏在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個有趣的案例啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究應該在這個事件處理完後再開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在消滅D-1才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了，紫東大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你在新的部門工作也沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在意的人，你會不會緊張呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣？最近？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前就是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我認識的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！好美的結晶石！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰送的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能已經讓他感到不舒服了\N因為那個印記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子…不冷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，因為我不是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，樹博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…久遠怎麼沒有來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她討厭寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的思念…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷的心是神媒柱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東大尉，紫東大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即到司令部\N今晚聚會見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直做得很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣，為什麼還要欺負我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七森君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不給我溫暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那塊結晶石…果然是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親、哥哥…不原諒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋發電機功能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為避免數據丟失進行數據中繼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換至緊急備用電源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在切換至緊急備用電源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然發生了緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它們！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19，在Y-MARK點確認到量子反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度大約500米，不，還在增長中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之前D-1相同的反應模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信它就是這次寒流的成因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守備失職，是這樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊！神名綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊？敵人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，他怎麼那樣說話！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來以後再抱怨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很快打倒它的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊，笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快反擊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣她會死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死？說什麼傻話！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，在那個Dolem裡面的…\N是小夜子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣擊毀它的話，\N小夜子小姐也會被殺的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我可做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀D-1最優先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人命無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在說什麼嗎？！你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TERRA可不是一個救生組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想救出七森君的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去創造一個奇跡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon被直接擊中！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon活動停止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示器無法顯示！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被人愛的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受我心中的寒意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會出事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是被選中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很溫暖，遙的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凍結的音色…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴弦跳動…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為眩目的光芒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從RahXephon那裡傳來高能量反應！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會創造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會創造的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做奇跡的那種東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靈魂的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認D-1已經消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認七森小夜子的生存反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常溫暖…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像太陽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種光…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起…對不起！對不起…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，在那次會議之後\N發生的事我都記不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,災難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士給我的掛墜…找不到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得收到那麼貴重的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿些飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一樣，藍色的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有去做定期檢查吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，olin很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:20:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可有點嫉妒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…是惠送給你的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，總一…我們的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂！小惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手套，非常暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙手套…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那入口通往許多扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門通向許多記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon 第九樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時之飼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界飽含著聲音


